Youtube Video Tutorial: https://youtu.be/1a6-QrmYf1M

Install Library: Pip Install bardapi
Github Link: https://github.com/dsdanielpark/Bard-API

Cookie Keys Needed:
__Secure-1PSID
__Secure-1PSIDTS
__Secure-1PSIDCC


Python Code:

from bardapi import BardCookies

cookie_dict = {
    "__Secure-1PSID": "xxx",
    "__Secure-1PSIDTS": "xxx",
    "__Secure-1PSIDCC": "xxx",
}

bard = BardCookies(cookie_dict=cookie_dict)
print(bard.get_answer("WHAT MODEL ARE YOU USING?")['content'])
